---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout>
  <main class="mt-20">
    <div class="flex gap-6 sm:gap-10">
      <Image src="/pug.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true" width="70" height="70" class="select-none pointer-events-none w-18 sm:w-[88px] h-auto" />
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-wider">
        I'm Axel
        <span class="block text-2xl sm:text-4xl text-base-400">Web Developer</span>
      </h1>
    </div>

    <p class="paragraph">
      I'm a self-taught developer based in <span class="highlight">Mexico</span> with
      <span class="highlight">2+ years</span> of experience who appreciates the finer details. My work sits at the intersection
      of <span class="highlight">performance</span> and <span class="highlight">aesthetics</span>. I'm passionate about
      <span class="highlight">clean code</span> and <span class="highlight">scalable architecture</span>.
    </p>

    <p class="paragraph">
      Starting in <span class="highlight">2018</span>, I've been exploring the full web ecosystem, building expertise in
      both <span class="highlight">frontend interactivity</span> and <span class="highlight">backend logic</span>. I
      also spend time exploring different development environments beyond the web.
    </p>

    <a href="/cv_axel_vasquez.pdf" target="_blank" class="text-lg tracking-wide text-base-400 leading-10">
      Download my CV
    </a>
  </main>
</Layout>
